{"tid":1094088,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"預計10年內，交通將會有革命性改變","createTime":"2019-04-06T04:51:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T18:11:38.000Z","uid":246823,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2566505d319938ff4f5ae333965e31be7fa8b12c","tid":1094088,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T04:51:15.000Z","msg":"如果說將來經過一場交通革命後，人類日常主要交通仍要依靠車輪，那麼就不可說是革命了。<br />\n<br />\n就如智能電話為通訊帶來改變一樣，交通工具亦應該會出現革命性的改變。而隨住相關科技日漸成熟，這場革命可能會在不出10年之內發生。<br />\n<br />\n交通工具雖然在過去有不少速度上的突破，例如磁浮，Hyperloop 等，但它們都無法「離地」。直到近年有人想出用無人機載人，未來交通的景象才有少少展露出來。<br />\n<br />\nHoverbike 已經有得賣<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/10/29/21/5550304-6330787-image-a-22_1540849242515.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F10%2F29%2F21%2F5550304-6330787-image-a-22_1540849242515.jpg&h=1439dc37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">The Russian built craft, which has already been sold to the Dubai Police force, has been redesigned with a new battery and carbon fiber frame.</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-6330787/The-150-000-HOVERBIKE-Scorpion-quadcopter-craft-available-preorder.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fsciencetech%2Farticle-6330787%2FThe-150-000-HOVERBIKE-Scorpion-quadcopter-craft-available-preorder.html&d=174aH8n0e8hd5Ixdtq%2FhYkKa%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=f5421f6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-6330787/The-150-000-HOVERBIKE-Scorpion-quadcopter-craft-available-preorder.html</a></span><br />\n<br />\n雖然 Hoverbike 的售價遠遠未達到大眾化的價錢；政策，法律及安全準則還未制定，但這些都是可以解決的問題。<br />\n<br />\n然而 Hoverbike 只是其中一種已知的飛行器，其他還有 Jetpack, Flyboard 等近年冒起的發明。可以不難想像將來天空佈滿飛行器，佔據不同的航行高度。將來的駕使系統亦會令各飛行器進行互相溝通，防止碰撞之餘又會分享數據，令飛行更安全同提升效率。"},{"pid":"f9fbcd32af134feb3ec5f4caac93e5015c63ff5b","tid":1094088,"uid":26601,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T04:53:41.000Z","msg":"ON9 design<br />\n軍用無問題<br />\n民用變成移動斷頭台"},{"pid":"1fb3a5f587c61cf252feaf294a4b5c017276f93c","tid":1094088,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T04:54:45.000Z","msg":"電單車飛行版<br />\n買多幾味餸再買埋尿片紙巾已經企咗喺度"},{"pid":"2bbec45945ca59511aba665356f897e957e29059","tid":1094088,"uid":57410,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T04:55:15.000Z","msg":"嘩眾取寵嘅標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9a4d75af2efec1546e564df0299968f02c29ca","tid":1094088,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T04:59:20.000Z","msg":"普及再多10年"},{"pid":"7efa18d7262ce502177d4060bc463b8724be28b2","tid":1094088,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T05:02:03.000Z","msg":"Hoverboard都未有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf879567c3d42c90282d8242ddf4c6225908e9b5","tid":1094088,"uid":8313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T05:02:17.000Z","msg":"可以飛呢已經顛覆傳統陸上交通，普及有一定難道，尤其係有關航空安全問題"},{"pid":"517e7e4b7d90c02db24465eafbd648dd202e396b","tid":1094088,"uid":3241,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T05:03:29.000Z","msg":"10年前已經講航空的士<br />\n而家呢， 連坐車比visa都未做到"},{"pid":"106a5b88bc5a8ca05464a6dfb5b32db23ef18fe7","tid":1094088,"uid":31715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T05:34:09.000Z","msg":"USD 150000 咁平既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26cf78fe0ea02d4bb3f7176de25486edc6800d1a","tid":1094088,"uid":140452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf879567c3d42c90282d8242ddf4c6225908e9b5","tid":1094088,"uid":8313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T05:02:17.000Z","msg":"可以飛呢已經顛覆傳統陸上交通，普及有一定難道，尤其係有關航空安全問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T12:43:30